pulses.name: 20241112 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
12 Nov 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US) - A significant number of attacks originate from the US, including multiple instances of the SystemBC botnet and JAWS DVR shell command execution.
- Hong Kong (HK) - Numerous attacks, particularly involving HTTP URI SQL injection and web server password file access, indicating a concentrated effort in exploiting web vulnerabilities.
- India (IN) - Notable for various remote command execution vulnerabilities, especially related to D-Link devices and multiple routers.
